content:
You can now use the Is Blank operator in a condition to check whether a text value contains no characters or only white space. For values of data types other than text, the Is Blank operator checks whether the values are null.

Where: This change applies to Lightning Experience in Enterprise, Performance, Unlimited, and Developer editions.

How: Add a Stage element, a Decision element, or Step resource to your orchestration. To determine whether a text resource references an empty string, configure a condition with a resource that can contain a string. Then select the Is Blank operator.
title: Streamline Salesforce Flows with Enhanced Conditions
